{"tid":297011,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"求救！懷疑底板壞咗","createTime":"2017-06-25T06:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T07:09:09.000Z","uid":113199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c70088baeff2affd90fac5bdd16077267f3db8eb","tid":297011,"uid":113199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:10:13.000Z","msg":"底板用緊ASUS B85M-G<br />\n呢排開機會響一長四短 跟住彈CPU FAN ERROR<br />\n咁差唔多一個禮拜開機都係咁 馬照跑舞照跳 <br />\n照打BF4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啱啱手痕拆開睇下咩事先發覺CPU FAN真係唔郁<br />\n再睇下原來連顯示卡FAN都唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開機個CPU FAN係有通電 <br />\n郁左一郁 之後斷斷續續郁少少 郁少少咁<br />\n唔理個error 入桌面個fan開始識行返 但望得出好慢<br />\n<br />\n顯示卡fan就有燈著 好似有見佢郁左一郁 但之後fan都係完全冇動靜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCPU FAN：Tranquillo Rev.4<br />\n顯示卡：MSI GTX1060 GAMING X 6G<br />\n以上都係半年多D前換 反而老母板就用左好幾年<br />\n<br />\n其實係咪真係老母板壞?對pc唔太熟 唔識逐樣試<br />\n亦都冇第二部機俾我試<br />\n<br />\n求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f150932feec08f304c03aef88711bf553c0a21","tid":297011,"uid":56328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:15:43.000Z","msg":"呢張顯示卡低過60度唔轉係正常, CPU FAN唔轉就唔正常"},{"pid":"81e158f397ab5e66704d1a75aebdfe7bc7b3189f","tid":297011,"uid":113199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:23:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢張顯示卡低過60度唔轉係正常, CPU FAN唔轉就唔正常</blockquote><br />\n係喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一直都冇留意到添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd53c243dfb1bed466babffe84e006d0edaa4365","tid":297011,"uid":113199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:26:59.000Z","msg":"個cpu fan原來自己上返500rpm左右 <br />\n咁到底開機唔識著係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b85c1595f70938e4adf827b72f1754f00f8ee3","tid":297011,"uid":56328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:34:08.000Z","msg":"有冇野KICK住?用手撩下佢順唔順?<br />\n識唔識RESET BIOS試下?<br />\n<br />\n如果都係唔識轉通常都係供電問題啦, 多數係底板問題多, 再來係火牛問題"},{"pid":"685c66735fbcb57a81fb3f59bf60f9cc3f828c02","tid":297011,"uid":25845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:40:45.000Z","msg":"樓主咩牛<br />\n試下用第二隻牛著機先"},{"pid":"cf76d87a3edf7c413a5690ce0e85ce3fff907d97","tid":297011,"uid":113199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T07:09:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇野KICK住?用手撩下佢順唔順?<br />\n識唔識RESET BIOS試下?<br />\n<br />\n如果都係唔識轉通常都係供電問題啦, 多數係底板問題多, 再來係火牛問題</blockquote><br />\n順 冇野kick住<br />\n<blockquote>樓主咩牛<br />\n試下用第二隻牛著機先</blockquote><br />\n冇第二隻牛 用緊maxpower 500w或5xx"}]}